msgid "Employees"
msgstr "Dipendenti"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/employees.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo **Employees** centralizes :doc:`personnel files <employees/"
"new_employee>`, employment :doc:`contracts <payroll/contracts>`, "
"and :doc:`departmental hierarchies <employees/departments>` in one system. "
"In addition, each employee record tracks :doc:`certifications <employees/"
"certifications>` and :doc:`training <employees/learning>`, "
"earned :doc:`badges <employees/badges>`, and all assigned :doc:`equipment "
"<employees/equipment>`. Customizable :doc:`onboarding <employees/"
"onboarding>` and :doc:`offboarding <employees/offboarding>` programs ensure "
"all employees are trained and ready for work, and all required steps are "
"taken when they leave."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **Dipendenti** centralizza :doc:`fascicoli del personale <employees/"
"new_employee>`, :doc:`contratti <payroll/contracts>` di lavoro "
"e :doc:`gerarchie dipartimentali <employees/departments>` in un unico "
"sistema. Inoltre, ogni scheda dipendente tiene traccia "
"di :doc:`certificazioni <employees/certifications>` e :doc:`formazione "
"<employees/learning>`, :doc:`badge <employees/badges>` acquisiti e tutte "
"le :doc:`attrezzature <employees/equipment>` assegnate. Programmi "
"personalizzabili di :doc:`onboarding <employees/onboarding>` "
"e :doc:`offboarding <employees/offboarding>` garantiscono che tutti i "
"dipendenti siano formati e pronti al lavoro, e che vengano eseguite tutte le "
"procedure necessarie quando lasciano l'azienda."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/employees.rst:16
msgid ""
"Properly configuring the settings in the **Employees** app ensures the "
"dashboard shows each employee's real-time attendance and work location—data "
"that drives payroll accuracy, capacity planning, and compliance reporting."
msgstr ""
"La corretta configurazione delle impostazioni nell'app **Dipendenti** "
"garantisce che la dashboard mostri la presenza in tempo reale di ciascun "
"dipendente e la posizione di lavoro, dati che guidano l'accuratezza del "
"libro paga, la pianificazione della capacità e la reportistica di conformità."

