"**Electronic signature file** (e.g., FS.DMFA.112768.20250109.00014.R.1.1) "
"(only for real declarations, not tests)"
msgstr ""
"**File di firma elettronica** (ad es., FS.DMFA.112768.20250109.00014.R.1.1) "
