#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:5
msgid "Hong Kong"
msgstr "Hong Kong"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:10
msgid ""
"The Hong Kong payroll localization ensures all salary computations strictly "
"comply with the `Employment Ordinance (Cap. 57) <https://www.labour.gov.hk/"
"eng/legislat/content2.htm>`_ and `Inland Revenue Department (IRD) <https://"
"www.ird.gov.hk/eng/ese/erc.htm>`_ requirements. This includes automated "
"calculations for |MPF| contributions, the generation of IR56 reports, and "
"the processing of leave payments such as Payment in Lieu of Notice, "
"Severance Payments (SP), and Long Service Payments (LSP)—fully updated for "
"the 2025 |MPF| offsetting transition rules."
msgstr ""
"La localizzazione del libro paga di Hong Kong garantisce che tutti i calcoli "
"salariali siano rigorosamente conformi all'`Employment Ordinance (Cap. 57) "
"<https://www.labour.gov.hk/eng/legislat/content2.htm>`_ e ai requisiti "
"dell'`Inland Revenue Department (IRD) <https://www.ird.gov.hk/eng/ese/"
"erc.htm>`_. Ciò include calcoli automatizzati per i contributi |MPF|, la "
"generazione di report IR56 e l'elaborazione dei pagamenti per ferie come il "
"Payment in Lieu of Notice, i Severance Payments (SP) e i Long Service "
"Payments (LSP), completamente aggiornati per le regole di transizione sulla "
"compensazione |MPF| del 2025."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:18
msgid ""
"Before configuring the Hong Kong localization, refer to the "
"general :doc:`payroll <../../payroll>` documentation. It covers foundational "
"information applicable to all localizations, including universal settings, "
"salary structures, and global payroll fields."
msgstr ""
"Prima di configurare la localizzazione di Hong Kong, consultare la "
"documentazione generale sul :doc:`libro paga <../../payroll>`. Copre le "
"informazioni fondamentali applicabili a tutte le localizzazioni, incluse le "
"impostazioni universali, le strutture salariali e i campi globali del libro "
"paga."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:27
msgid ""
":ref:`Install <general/install>` the following modules to get all the "
"features of the Hong Kong payroll localization:"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Installare <general/install>` i seguenti moduli per ottenere tutte le "
