#~ msgid ""
#~ "The Hong Kong payroll localization ensures all salary computations "
#~ "strictly comply with the `Employment Ordinance (Cap. 57) <https://"
#~ "www.labour.gov.hk/eng/legislat/content2.htm>`_ and `Inland Revenue "
#~ "Department (IRD) <https://www.ird.gov.hk/eng/ese/erc.htm>`_ requirements. "
#~ "This includes automated calculations for Mandatory Provident Fund (MPF) "
#~ "contributions, the generation of IR56 reports, and the processing of "
#~ "leave payments such as Payment in Lieu of Notice, Severance Payments "
#~ "(SP), and Long Service Payments (LSP)—fully updated for the 2025 MPF "
#~ "offsetting transition rules."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "La localizzazione del libro paga di Hong Kong garantisce che tutti i "
#~ "calcoli salariali siano rigorosamente conformi ai requisiti della "
#~ "`Employment Ordinance (Cap. 57) <https://www.labour.gov.hk/eng/legislat/"
#~ "content2.htm>`_ e dell'`Inland Revenue Department (IRD) <https://"
#~ "www.ird.gov.hk/eng/ese/erc.htm>`_. Ciò include calcoli automatizzati per "
#~ "i contributi al Mandatory Provident Fund (MPF), la generazione di report "
#~ "IR56 e l'elaborazione dei pagamenti per ferie come Payment in Lieu of "
#~ "Notice, Severance Payments (SP) e Long Service Payments (LSP), "
#~ "completamente aggiornati per le regole di transizione dell'offsetting MPF "
#~ "del 2025."

